flowchart TD
    A([Start: ReportGenerator]) --> B[Inputs<br/>results, old_info, new_info, format]

    %% -------- CONFIG --------
    B --> C[Resolve format<br/>config.format or override]

    C --> D{Format type}

    %% -------- FORMAT SWITCH --------
    D -->|pretty| E1[Pretty formatter]
    D -->|json| E2[JSON formatter]
    D -->|markdown| E3[Markdown formatter]
    D -->|text| E4[Text formatter]
    D -->|other| E1

    %% -------- PRETTY PIPELINE --------
    E1 --> P1[Build Overview Panel<br/>severity, rows, columns, paths]

    P1 --> P2{summary_only?}

    P2 -- No --> P3[Add Drift Details<br/>schema + row tables]
    P3 --> P4[Add Type Changes Table]
    P4 --> P5[Add Explanations Panel]

    P2 -- Yes --> P6[Skip detailed sections]

    P5 --> P7
    P6 --> P7

    P7{output_file set?}
    P7 -- Yes --> P8[Add export message]
    P7 -- No --> P9[Skip export note]

    P8 --> P10[Join all sections]
    P9 --> P10

    %% -------- JSON --------
    E2 --> J1[Build structured dict<br/>files, severity, schema, types, rows]
    J1 --> J2[Convert to JSON string]

    %% -------- MARKDOWN --------
    E3 --> M1[Build markdown report]
    M1 --> M2[Sections:<br/>summary, schema, types, rows, insights]

    %% -------- TEXT --------
    E4 --> T1[Build plain text report]
    T1 --> T2[Sections:<br/>header, schema, types, rows, insights]

    %% -------- OUTPUT --------
    P10 --> Z
    J2 --> Z
    M2 --> Z
    T2 --> Z

    Z[Final Report String] --> Y{Save report?}

    Y -- Yes --> Y1[Write to file<br/>create dirs if needed]
    Y -- No --> Y2[Return output only]

    Y1 --> END([End])
    Y2 --> END
